_sText:
This is my first release for a while, I just wanted to get something out. 
I started this map a while ago and just only finished the layout. I still need to fix some bugs for the final. Also I would love to have any constructive feedback so I can make the final better.

Bug and todo list:
- Some reflection errors (if anyone know how to fix them then can you say)
- Some better brushwork in areas. 
- Some better detail and more detailed smaller brushwork.
- Maybe some more better hiding areas in the big storage room.
- Some different sorts of zombie mod gameplay within the map.

Thanks, drimp

Note: Please tell me if you add it to a server
